descript.abstract: Park Boundaries: A simplified polygon layer of California State Parks Boundaries, providing Unit name, subtype and other attributes. California State Park Boundaries are for reference and not for official or legal property boundary determination. Current as of February 28, 2022.
descript.purpose: Representation of the location of State Parks boundaries.
